description:
As a merchant
  I want to create store pick up order manually
name: Store pick up manually create order

elements.name: Store pick up manually create order

steps.name: I am on Admin Login Page
I fill correct account email to email field
I fill correct account password to password field
I click on login button
I should see successful login
I check intercom message notification frame and click clear intercom message button
I check intercom message notification frame and click intercom message close button
I check new feature alert notification frame and click new feature alert close button
I check and click exclude products panel close button
I check and click no thanks button
I am on Orders Create Page
I click on new customer button
I fill name to name field
I fill email to email field
I fill phone to phone number field
I click on next button
I should see select product button
I click on select product button
I input '15th Product for Checkout' to search product field
1st row of select product should contain '15th Product for Checkout'

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"15th Product for Checkout","expectText":"15th Product for Checkout"}

steps.name: I click on 1st row of select product
I click on ok save button
I should see product next button
I click on product next button
I should see shipping destination dropdown
I select shipping destination dropdown option included 'Taiwan' of shipping destination dropdown

steps.name: I should see same as customer info checkbox
I click on same as customer info checkbox
I select store pick up city dropdown option included 'Taipei City' of store pick up city dropdown
I should not see store pick up area dropdown
I should not see store pick up district dropdown
I select store pick up store name dropdown option included "Daan store 2 - No. 666, Sec. 1, Da\'an Rd.," of store pick up store name dropdown

steps.name: I click on delivery next button
I should see payment method dropdown
I select payment method dropdown option included 'Custom' of payment method dropdown
I wait for 3 seconds for loading
I should see create order button
I click on create order button
I should be redirected to Orders Show Page
delivery method should contain "Store Pick-up"
delivery address should contain "Delivery AddressNo. 666, Sec. 1, Da\'an Rd.,"

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"Delivery AddressNo. 666, Sec. 1, Da'an Rd.,","expectText":"Delivery AddressNo. 666, Sec. 1, Da'an Rd.,"}

steps.name: ---ROLL BACK---
I am on Delivery Options Page
I click delete button of delivery method list for the same order of row of delivery options list included 'dirty data'
I should see delete confirmation popover
I click on delete checkbox
I click on confirm delete button
1st row of delivery options list should not contain "Store Pick-up"
